Allelic deletion at chromosome bands 11q14-23 is common in neuroblastoma.

Maris JM(1), Guo C, White PS, Hogarty MD, Thompson PM, Stram DO, Gerbing R, 
Matthay KK, Seeger RC, Brodeur GM.
